      Find the
      
          y-intercepts
        
      for each of the following equations.
    </p><ul><li><m> y \times -8 + x \times -4 = 3 </m></li><li><m> y \times -3 + x \times -8 = -4 </m></li></ul></statement><answer><ul><li><m> -\frac{3}{8} </m></li><li><m> \frac{4}{3} </m></li></ul></answer></exercise>
